\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I was just wondering. You said that\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 \u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Now hold on. I want to know what you\u8217\'92re on my lucky rocks for?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I was just wondering.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Don\u8217\'92t be out here wondering,\u8221\'94 Tob said. \u8220\'93Wondering about other people and what they\u8217\'92ve got will get you into trouble. So you just worry bout your rocks and I\u8217\'92ll worry bout mine.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I warned you not to get him started,\u8221\'94 Moteah muttered.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Get me started?\u8221\'94 Tob said in offense. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m not started. I\u8217\'92m just tryin to keep the boy focused on what\u8217\'92s he needs to be focused on, and that\u8217\'92s his own damned luck.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Alright, alright,\u8221\'94 Mandri said, trying to calm Tob down. \u8220\'93What should I do then? How should I test my new rock?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What do you want to do?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mandri thought for a moment. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Well, I\u8217\'92d like to get up and get out of this cave.\u8221\'94}
